98
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:03,790
Berhenti!

99
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,320
Tuan Muda!

100
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,210
Hutan begitu besar.

101
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:15,840
