aku sebagai lawan.

210
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:29,320
Benar tidak, Saudara Tang?

211
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:31,320
Aku tak ada kesempatan lagi.

212
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:32,840
Aku harap ucapan Master benar.

213
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,380
