214
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,200
-Ada yang masuk ke tanganku.
-Tang San!

215
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:43,910
Bertahanlah.

216
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:47,790
-Tang San!
-Tak tahu diri.

217
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:52,760
Karena kau tidak dengarkan aku,
maka mati saja sendiri!

218
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:01,880
Bawa dia pergi.

219
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,960
Kau…

220
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:09,960
Bukannya kau pekerja di akademi itu?!

221
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,280
Ternyata, kau yang bantu mereka!

222
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,320
Pergi? Bagaimana mereka akan pergi?

223
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,200
Keberuntungan bagai petir.

224
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:19,740
Kau bilang apa?

225
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:21,790
Hancurkan.

226
00:12:22,590 --> 00:12:23,400
Sudah gila, ya?

227
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:26,000
Luo Sanpao!

228
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:32,230
Pergi!

